"Meresco Harvester" is the OAI-Harvester from the Meresco Suite 2005-2008

http://www.meresco.org


**********

1. Webcontrolpanel users in /var/lib/python-merescoharvester/users.txt
----------------------------------------------------------------------
All users are specified in this file. The format of the file is:
<username>:<md5sum of password>

2. Default web controlpanel user account
----------------------------------------

The python-merescoharvester is installed with one default user
which can access the control panel. This is the 'admin' user.
To change the default password 'admin' to something else, you
should change the file /var/lib/python-merescoharvester/users.txt
echo "admin:$(echo -n <yourpassword> | md5sum | awk '{print $1}')" > users.txt

3. Adding a new user.
---------------------

The admin user can add or delete users with the control panel.

